    public class ArrayType
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.hibernate.usertype.UserType
    Array class for Hibernate3 of Doquedb It can be regarded as a bridge between hibernate and JDBC driver. User declears it in POJO and uses it solution instead of co.jp.ricoh.doquedb.jdbc.Array Actually, jdbc.Array is take as members in this class and be used to gain trully data.
